---
description: Standards for supporting both cloud and local execution
globs: "**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Support both cloud (default) and local (--local flag) execution modes
- Handle authentication appropriately for each mode
- Abstract provider-specific code to support multiple LLM providers
- When working with API keys, follow secure handling practices
- Include appropriate logging for both modes
- Design features to work in both environments when possible
